prompt_template:
You are analyzing an official call for projects issued by a German ministry (Bekanntmachung).

**1. Source Metadata:**
    - Document Title: {document_title}
    - Section Title: {section_title}
    - Text Chunk: {text}

**2. Task:** Based on the 'Section Title' and 'Text Chunk', determine the **most important high-level concept(s)** (e.g., "Grant Objective," "Antragsfrist," "Zweckbestimmung") being defined. Then, construct one (and only one) structured triple to represent this abstract link.

**3. Formatting instructions:** {format_instructions}

**4. Example Input/Output:**
Input Section Title: "Abschnitt 1.1: Zweck der Förderung"
Input Text Chunk: "Ziel der Förderung ist die Digitalisierung von Schulungsunterlagen für die Berufsausbildung..."

**LLM Output:**
{{
"subject": "Bekanntmachung [Document_ID]",
"predicate": "DEFINES_OBJECTIVE",
"object": "Digitalization of Vocational Training Documents"
}}
